-nh%E1%BA%A5t-v%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-%C3%94-T%C3%B4n-b%E1%BB%99i-%C4%91ao/poem-9jh_w7dJgtuO758ktvH2eQ">Thôi Ngũ Lục đồ bình phong các phú nhất vật đắc Ô Tôn bội đao - 崔五六圖屏風各賦一物得烏孫佩刀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-cung/poem-KChMkcaPIRWltfARjtoiVA">Vịnh cung - 詠弓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/author-19Y6ZR7qO5ib1Hce98JOUQ">Lý Thế Dân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%E1%BB%8Dng-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-WqJvkXl9a2ORHiddnRzsKw">Vọng Tương Sơn tự - 望湘山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/Vu-s%C6%A1n-cao/poem-nkLK983trvV6S_1lIDQRkA">Vu sơn cao - 巫山高</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90oan/author-vHSGJ24Oq83oesxet8BFJA">Lý Đoan</a>)<br></div>	</div>
